---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Our Team - Blue Logic Water"
  description="Meet the local team behind Blue Logic Water. Wasatch-born, professionally certified, dedicated to bringing pure water to Salt Lake City homes."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Team</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Wasatch-born water purification experts</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Wasatch-Born Story</h2>
      <p class="story-text">
        Blue Logic Water was founded by a team of engineers and water quality
        specialists who grew up in the Salt Lake Valley. We experienced
        firsthand the challenges of Utah's hard water and the frustration of
        seeing families pay inflated prices for basic water purification.
      </p>
      <p class="story-text">
        Our mission is simple: bring commercial-grade reverse osmosis technology
        to homes at a fair price. No marketing gimmicks, no unnecessary
        upsells—just pure water and honest service.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Meet the Team</h2>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-photo">
            <div class="placeholder-photo">Photo</div>
          </div>
          <h3>Lead Installer & Technician</h3>
          <p class="role">Professional Installation Specialist</p>
          <p>
            Licensed and certified with over a decade of experience in water
            purification systems. Ensures every installation meets
            commercial-grade standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-photo">
            <div class="placeholder-photo">Photo</div>
          </div>
          <h3>Water Quality Engineer</h3>
          <p class="role">System Design & Optimization</p>
          <p>
            Specializes in RO system engineering and water chemistry. Designs
            custom solutions for Utah's unique water profile and mineral
            content.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-photo">
            <div class="placeholder-photo">Photo</div>
          </div>
          <h3>Customer Success Lead</h3>
          <p class="role">Client Relations & Support</p>
          <p>
            Dedicated to ensuring every client receives exceptional service from
            first contact through installation and beyond. Local Salt Lake City
            resident.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guarantee">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Purity Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="guarantee-intro">
        When we enter your home, we follow the Blue Logic code of conduct:
      </p>

      <div class="guarantee-grid">
        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Professional Excellence</h3>
          <p>
            Every installation is performed to commercial standards with
            meticulous attention to detail.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Respect Your Home</h3>
          <p>
            We treat your home as our own—clean workspace, protective equipment,
            and thorough cleanup.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Transparent Communication</h3>
          <p>
            Clear explanations of the work, no hidden fees, and honest timelines
            from start to finish.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Local Accountability</h3>
          <p>
            We're your neighbors. Our reputation is built on trust and we stand
            behind every installation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Ongoing Support</h3>
          <p>
            We don't disappear after installation. Local service and maintenance
            support when you need it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-item">
          <h3>Fair Pricing Always</h3>
          <p>
            No upsells, no pressure tactics. Just honest pricing for honest
            work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="local">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Proudly Serving the Wasatch Front</h2>
      <p>
        From Park City to Draper, we serve families throughout the Salt Lake
        Valley with professional-grade water purification solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Service Areas:</strong> Salt Lake City • Park City • Draper • Sandy
        • Cottonwood Heights • Holladay • Murray • Millcreek
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Work With a Local Team</h2>
      <p>Schedule a free consultation with our water quality experts</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      oklch(0.95 0.01 90) 0%,
      oklch(0.85 0.05 220) 100%
    );
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container.center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .story {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .story-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  .team-section {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .team-member {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .member-photo {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: oklch(0.9 0.01 90);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .placeholder-photo {
    color: oklch(0.6 0.02 270);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .team-member h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .role {
    color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .team-member p:not(.role) {
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .guarantee {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .guarantee-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .guarantee-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .guarantee-item {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .guarantee-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: oklch(0.2 0.02 270);
  }

  .guarantee-item p {
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .local {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .local p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .team-grid,
    .guarantee-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
